OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA few mist and fog patches
OL,6,Fwhich will be quick to clear in the
OL,7,Fmorning to leave a dry and settled day
OL,8,Fwith light winds and plenty of sunny
OL,9,Fspells.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FMostly dry with some late
OL,12,Fsunshine at first this evening then
OL,13,Fclear spells after sunset. Becoming
OL,14,Fcloudier overnight but remaining dry.
OL,15,FMostly light winds, breezy around the
OL,16,Fcoast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
