OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FA cloudy morning with the odd
OL,6,Fisolated shower possible. Cloud
OL,7,Fbreaking up through the afternoon to
OL,8,Fgive long sunny periods. Breezy near
OL,9,Fthe coast.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FHigh
OL,12,Fpressure dominates bringing a dry and
OL,13,Fsettled few days. Cloudy at times but
OL,14,Fplenty of long sunny spells. Breezy on
OL,15,FWednesday then winds falling light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
